      "content": "Based on the search results, the most relevant link for obtaining Mercedes Sosa's discography is the Wikipedia page titled \"Mercedes Sosa - Wikipedia\".\n\nNext, I will scrape the Wikipedia page for Mercedes Sosa to extract the discography section, and then identify the studio albums published between 2000 and 2009.\n\nI'll use the `scrape_wikipedia_tables` function to extract the necessary data from the Wikipedia page and analyze it.\n\nHere is the code to scrape the table data from the Wikipedia page:\n\n```python\nfrom functions import scrape_wikipedia_tables\n\n# URL of the Wikipedia page\nurl = \"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mercedes_Sosa\"\n\n# Keyword to find the relevant table\nheader_keyword = \"Discography\"\n\n# Scrape the Wikipedia table\ntable_data = scrape_wikipedia_tables(url, header_keyword)\nprint(table_data)\n```\n\nComputer_terminal, please run this code to scrape the table data from the Wikipedia page."
